OL,4,Cschoolgirl, 14, granted bail
OL,6,FA mother who has been jointly charged
OL,7,Fwith murdering her teenage daughter
OL,8,Fhas been granted bail.
OL,10,FScarlett Vickers, 14, was allegedly
OL,11,Fstabbed in the family home in Geneva
OL,12,FRoad, Darlington, on Friday.
OL,14,FHer parents Simon Vickers, 49, and
OL,15,FSarah Hall, 44, have both been charged
OL,16,Fwith her murder.
OL,18,FHall appeared at Teesside Crown Court
OL,19,Fvia a video link from prison on
OL,20,FWednesday 10 July and an application
OL,21,Fwas made for her to be given bail.
