OL,4,Cschoolgirl, 14, granted bail
OL,6,FMr Justice Jacobs granted the
OL,7,Fapplication, with certain conditions,
OL,8,Fincluding that she stay with a family
OL,9,Fmember and abide by a curfew.
OL,11,FNo application was made on behalf of
OL,12,FVickers.
OL,14,FA pre-trial hearing has been scheduled
OL,15,Ffor 5 August at the same court, with a
OL,16,Ftrial date provisionally set for 14
OL,17,FJanuary.
OL,19,FScarlett was a pupil at Haughton
OL,20,FAcademy in Darlington.
