OL,6,FIn a tribute, the school said: "She
OL,7,Fwas always immaculately turned out,
OL,8,Frespectful and polite.
OL,10,F"A very friendly girl with a great
OL,11,Fsense of humour, she was popular with
OL,12,Fher friends and will be greatly missed
OL,13,Fby everyone at school.
OL,15,F"Staff and pupils at Haughton Academy
OL,16,Fand the Education Village Academy
OL,17,FTrust are extremely saddened by the
OL,18,Fnews and we would like to pass on our
OL,19,Fthoughts to everyone affected by this
OL,20,Ftragedy.
